'''隼砲'''（[[英語|英語]]：''Falconet''或''Falcon''），也译作'''鹰炮'''，是一種輕型的[[加農砲|加農砲]]，大約出現於十五世紀晚期至十七世紀<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefreedictionary.com/falconet |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-11-11 |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025172227/https://www.thefreedictionary.com/falconet |dead-url=no }}</ref>，用法類似於野戰砲，在大航海時代，許多探險用的船也會裝上它。在中世紀時，銃砲常用爬蟲或鳥獸的名字來描述，也會將其形象雕刻或鑄在上面。隼砲發射的砲彈質量與隼相當，並且經常有隼的裝飾雕紋，所以以[[隼|隼]]來命名。
<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.regimental-art.com/history_greys.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417105736/http://www.regimental-art.com/history_greys.htm# |archive-date=2015-04-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=History of the Scots Greys|url=http://www.regimental-art.com/history_greys.htm|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417105736/http://www.regimental-art.com/history_greys.htm|archive-date=2015-04-17|access-date=2017-08-09|website=Regimental-art.com}}</ref>

隼砲的砲管長約1.2公尺，口徑約5公分，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.probertencyclopaedia.com/cgi-bin/res.pl?keyword=Falconet&offset=0 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2008-08-26 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080504235643/http://www.probertencyclopaedia.com/cgi-bin/res.pl?keyword=Falconet&offset=0 |archive-date=2008-05-04 }}</ref>質量約80至200公斤，使用約230克的黑火藥，發射約450克的圓形砲彈。最大射程約1500公尺。<ref name="ATTA">{{cite web|url=http://www.nps.gov/history/history/online_books/source/is3/is3c.htm|title=Artillery through the ages|website=Nps.gov|access-date=2017-08-09|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070705183936/http://www.nps.gov/history/history/online_books/source/is3/is3c.htm|archive-date=2007-07-05}}</ref><ref name="EO">{{cite web|url=http://www.littlewoodham.org.uk/research/ord.htm|title=Littlewoodham|website=Littlewoodham.org.uk|access-date=2017-08-09|archive-date=2010-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100825043348/http://www.littlewoodham.org.uk/research/ord.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>也可以發射[[葡萄彈|葡萄彈]]（由許多小彈丸組成的砲彈，類似[[散彈|散彈]]）。
